Photo Forum Photo Forum Members enjoy exclusive invitations to all VIP exhibition opening events at MoPA. Opportunities for collecting and learning will be afforded through fascinating local and national photography-focused adventures. Members at this level will also enjoy one private Salon reception with a renowned artist each year.
